data.description: Searching for a home in Vermilion? Check out this gorgeous custom built home located in one of the most desired Vermilion developments, Indian Ridge Estates! The development offers indoor pool, clubhouse, fitness center, tennis and basketball courts. Just a few minutes from downtown Vermilion, shops, restaurants, marinas, beaches & Lake Erie! This custom designed ranch is an absolute must see! Shows like a model home. This home offers 2095 square feet of living space and an additional 1800 square foot finished basement with an oversized 4th bedroom, walk-in closet, and attached full bathroom. All completed by Amish craftsmen after the build. The basement buildout offers a huge open concept. Bring your ideas such as a gameroom, movie area, or whatever your heart desires! The Palmer model ranch has an offset owner's suite with master bath, tiled walk in master shower, and walk in closet. There are 2 additional bedrooms on the opposite side of the house with a second full bath dividing the rooms. This house has so many other amazing features including a covered front entry with double glass entry door, large office with glass French doors,  great room, beautiful kitchen with quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, subway tile backsplash and vented hood range. Also, a laundry and mud room on the main floor, just off the two car garage that is equipped with a universal electric car charger. Additional features include a gas fireplace with grey stone front and custom, built-in display shelves. Additionally, LVP flooring throughout the main living area and upgraded carpet in all the bedrooms and basement, Pella double hung windows, and insulated garage add to all the features of this home. When exiting the back sliding glass door, you walk onto a lifetime deck followed by a stamped concrete patio surrounded by a quiet wooded lot. An area sure to entertain your guests for summer cookouts or dinner with the family!
